{
  "texts": [
    "5:Modify y according to soft variant (2) to obtain y wm.",
    "6:Recover x wm ← IDFT(y wm).",
    "7: end for 8: Collect each x wm to form a matrix X wm.",
    "9: Apply inverse standardization and inverse YJT to X wm, round and clip if needed, and release.to modify only the first half of the entries (i.e.",
    "m = ⌊ p-1 2 ⌋ entries), as the remaining values can be determined by conjugate symmetry."
  ]
}